Package: paneffectR
Title: Comparative Genomics of Effector Proteins Across Genome Assemblies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Dan", "MacLean", email = "dan.maclean@tsl.ac.uk",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-1174-3654"))
Author: Dan MacLean [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dan MacLean <dan.maclean@tsl.ac.uk>
Description: Clusters proteins from multiple genome assemblies into ortholog
    groups, builds presence/absence matrices, and generates publication-ready
    visualizations. Designed for effector protein analysis from the omnieff
    pipeline but works with any protein sets.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/USER/paneffectR, https://USER.github.io/paneffectR/
